  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<h3 class=\"big-one-two\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:28px;\">AMC8 華人區第一時間解題</span></strong></h3>\n<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">新加入的朋友<br />\nAMC8 華人區第一時間解題！<br />\nAMC8全球活動於11月16日正式結束，國際奧數2金1銀的獵豹老師團隊將於11月17日晚7-8:30為同學解析每個精彩題目，請大家準時收看直播。我們會在今天18:45給直播連結，Line直播點擊即可收看（無需下載）<br />\n今天再把連結放上來喔<br />\n回放已結束，謝謝大家</span></span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><a data-token-index=\"0\" href=\"https://youtu.be/4YMnsbU3KWU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" tabindex=\"0\">https://youtu.be/4YMnsbU3KWU</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/695704361382252/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/695704361382252/</a></span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<div class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-4by3\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4YMnsbU3KWU?rel=0\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span></p>\n\n<div class=\"edit\">\n<div class=\"edit\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
